{"tid":598096,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★微軟新招炒IT狗----微軟：女員工性騷擾投訴：已解雇20人","createTime":"2018-03-19T08:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T09:52:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1446e718589a78d4f5f24df98849ab484accb234","tid":598096,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:23:21.000Z","msg":"3月19日消息 前不久，IT之家報導了微軟女性員工的關於性別歧視與性騷擾的事件。微軟公司最近做出了回應，稱去年已<span style=\"color: red;\">因此解雇了20名員工</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上周，微軟公開了一封給公司員工的電子郵件。郵件中，微軟首席人才官Kathleen Hogan表示，2017年，在美國的6.5萬名微軟名員工中總共收到了83起性騷擾投訴。<br />\n<br />\n她說，在調查之後，至少有一半的員工表示了支持。還有一名員工因&ldquo;令人無法容忍的行為&rdquo;，超<span style=\"color: red;\">過一半的員工支持將他解雇</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/html/it/351676.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2Fhtml%2Fit%2F351676.htm&d=oK81T%2BzW%2FRBjANvf%2FMit2QtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=4a28ed60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/html/it/351676.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d4a60a20fb044429f94402bb441cea6cc7b5e62e","tid":598096,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:24:43.000Z","msg":"IT狗d毒撚Look，已是原罪"},{"pid":"75caeb7801722fb635e8db663aa1183ff31167a5","tid":598096,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"用完即棄 變得更方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa85f3eda1e636cd6124baccd036e1f866509a2b","tid":598096,"uid":18309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:26:36.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"e32d73200e6bb26cf481fd13407b59750a459575","tid":598096,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa85f3eda1e636cd6124baccd036e1f866509a2b","tid":598096,"uid":18309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:26:36.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:29:06.000Z","msg":"一句 metoo，IT狗即時瞓街乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal